      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。用户完成的是HealthTech_PatientRecords这个mission，然后前端去调API。这里API的路径是/journeys/{HealthTech_LabAnalyzer}/mint-badge对吗？还是说应该用PatientRecords作为参数？",
